1. *Razume* se da ćemo živeti bolje sutra (It is understood that we will live better tomorrow). 
2. Učenik *razume* šta profesor govori (The student understands what the professor is saying). 
3. Dete još uvek nije *razumelo* da se ne sme lomiti stvari (The child still hasn't understood that it is not allowed to break things).
4. *Razumevanje* je važno za uspešan život (Understanding is important for a successful life).